flowchart TB
    App[Target App · draw.io / iMovie<br/>closed UI — no API]

    subgraph P5["P5 · Portable, human-in-the-loop Studio"]
        User([User · Studio])
        Detector[Detector · OpenCV]
        Labeller[Labeller]
    end

    subgraph P1["P1 · Symbolic state over pixels"]
        UIGraph[(UI Graph · per interface)]
        SceneGraph[(Scene Graph · by id, not pixels)]
    end

    subgraph P2["P2 · Self-growing tool tree"]
        ToolTree[Tool Tree · L0/L1/L2 · auto-promote]
    end

    subgraph P3["P3 · Plan once, run deterministically"]
        Planner[Planner · full plan in 1 call]
        Orchestrator[Orchestrator · deterministic run]
    end

    subgraph P4["P4 · Checkpoint verify &amp; repair"]
        Critic[Critic · verify from screenshot]
    end

    User -->|capture| Detector
    Detector -->|boxes| Labeller
    Labeller -->|labels| UIGraph

    User -->|task| Planner
    SceneGraph --> Planner
    ToolTree --> Planner
    Planner -->|plan| Orchestrator
    Orchestrator -->|dispatch| ToolTree
    UIGraph -->|coords| ToolTree
    ToolTree -->|mouse &amp; keyboard| App
    App -->|reconcile| SceneGraph

    Orchestrator -->|screenshot| Critic
    Critic -->|verdict| Orchestrator
    Critic -.->|on fail: repair| Planner

    classDef agent fill:#2E6FB5,stroke:#1b4d80,color:#fff;
    class Labeller,Planner,Orchestrator,Critic agent;
